mistakes.correct_answer_markdown:
```cpp
long long qpow(long long a, long long b, long long p) {
  long long res = 1, base = a % p;
  while (b) {
    if (b & 1) res = res * base % p;
    base = base * base % p;
    b >>= 1;
  }
  return res;
}
```

